ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectHon. Cathy McLeod ** MP Travel **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Hon. CATHY MCLEOD, Member of Parliament, to travel to HELLS GATE 43111 TRANS CANADA HWY, BOSTON BAR, BRITISH COLUMBIA, on August 22, 2013, to attend an event commemorating the 100th anniversary of the Hells Gate rockslides, organized by the Pacific Salmon Commission, on behalf of the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans.
